Package io.dummymaker.annotation.special

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    GenEnumerate
    Generates numeric sequence from given number (default 0) to all produced/populated Dummies Works only when populate/produce list of dummies, not a single dummy
    GenForceExport
    Force object field to export, despite it been annotated with generate annotations
    GenIgnoreExport
    Ignores object field during export
    GenRenameExport
    Allow to rename fields and class names when export To rename class you should annotate its constructor
